            "x2": 1840,
            "y2": 2029
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 14,
        "text": "असंख्य कह्यो श्रुति जोई । वृहदारण्य माहिं कह्यो सोई ।। मल",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jnanadasa1895_09_textline_14.png",
